From: Kirill Kapranov <kirill.kapranov@compulab.co.il>
Date: Mon, 14 Feb 2022 00:46:25 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 40/40] dts:phy: Eliminate excessive reset

The eth phy is tuned on u-boot, however the reset at Linux boot cleans all the
tuning and makes the phy inoperable. Eliminate the reset at Linux boot so as to
preserve the phy tuned.

Signed-off-by: Kirill Kapranov <kirill.kapranov@compulab.co.il>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/compulab/ucm-imx8m-mini.dts | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/compulab/ucm-imx8m-mini.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/compulab/ucm-imx8m-mini.dts
index 77ebda255fc8..89b7ebfeef73 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/compulab/ucm-imx8m-mini.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/compulab/ucm-imx8m-mini.dts
@@ -80,6 +80,7 @@
 		regulator-always-on;
 		enable-active-high;
 		startup-delay-us = <500>;
+		regulator-boot-on;
 	};
 
 	regulator_bt_dev_wake: bt_dev_wake {
